What's gotten into you?

1625
01:29:59,828 --> 01:30:01,811
(SOBBING)

1626
01:30:06,502 --> 01:30:08,169
I thought
I'd lost you, Miguel.

1627
01:30:08,171 --> 01:30:09,835
MIGUEL: I'm sorry, <i>Papa.</i>

1628
01:30:09,837 --> 01:30:13,188
